Class FilteringDirectory

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.pl.util.FilteringDirectory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDirectory, IResource

    public class FilteringDirectory
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDirectory
    IDirectory implementation that returns only files with certain extensions. Used to filter out everything except rules out of config/ directory when running the server.
